##Naturalisation of your partner if they move to the UK

Your partner can apply to [become a British citizen](/becoming-a-british-citizen/if-your-spouse-is-a-british-citizen) once they’ve lived in the UK for 3 years.

If you’re entering an opposite sex civil partnership in Argentina, it might be recognised in England, Wales and Northern Ireland. You need to check with the [British embassy or high commission](/world/organisations/british-embassy-buenos-aires).